    <p>{`We made a stop at some castle, and a monastery, and a few random other spots but honestly I think they were all just pit stops on the way to Irelands west coast to see the main attraction- the Cliffs of Moher.`}</p>
    <p>{`Eventually we stopped in a small town for lunch, where because it was the end of tourist season there was apparently only one place open still. While it was really busy with the remaining tourist bus companies all dropping off their passengers here they were surprisingly quick and not a bad meal either.`}</p>
