    <p>{`Finally we were on our way to see the Cliffs of Moher and thankfully we had pretty good weather and they were incredible! As tall as the empire state building, the pictures don’t really do them justice. It was very windy here but we walked around for probably an hour soaking in the impressive sights.`}</p>
